# FinOps Operating System - Project Context

## Project Objective

Build an enterprise-grade, open-source FinOps Operating System that provides governance frameworks, operating models, templates, KPIs, dashboards, optimization playbooks, AI FinOps guidance, Kubernetes FinOps practices, FOCUS standards, unit economics models, automation patterns, and case studies.

The repository should align with current FinOps Foundation principles while remaining vendor-neutral and practical for enterprise adoption.

---

## Design Principles

* FinOps Foundation aligned
* Vendor neutral where possible
* Enterprise focused
* Practical and implementation oriented
* Humanized and professional
* No fabricated metrics or savings claims
* No arbitrary staffing models
* No invented maturity targets
* Business value focused
* Multi-cloud by design
* AI FinOps included
* Kubernetes FinOps included

